    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "ginger tea isn't going to fix my spine lol. i'm just looking for something that actually works so i can stop crying. i saw online that some people take higher doses for severe acute pain, like 1200mg or even 2000mg at once to get it under control. is that really that bad? if it's just for tonight i'll be fine, i just need the pain to stop so i can sleep.",
